snippet.title: JSW: The Sun Is No Longer Producing Heat walkthrough | ZX Spectrum | JSWCL-139
snippet.description:
A walkthrough of "JSW: The Sun Is No Longer Producing Heat", a 2002 ZX Spectrum game by Nick Aldridge.

The game's page on JSW Central is at https://jswcentral.org/jsw48-a-31_sunnoheat.html.
